@node Source

Source
******

I included the source-code of the proc-handler. It should be very useful
for people writing a filesystem or a handler.

You may use this source for anything you want, if you don't remove the
copyright and if you mention my name.

If you have any questions about the source, feel free to send me an email
(please no snail-mail).
@endnode


